    <item>
      <title>哈利法克斯称英国房价 10 月份创下历史新高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-07/uk-house-prices-climbed-to-record-high-in-october-halifax-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据一家领先的抵押贷款机构称，英国房价十月份创下了历史新高，这表明廉价抵押贷款带来的提振抵消了购房者在月底工党预算出台前产生的预算前忧虑。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-07/uk-house-prices-climbed-to-record-high-in-october-halifax-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Nov 2024 07:07:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
