      <title>6500 亿欧元外流是德国政治动荡的核心</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-07/germany-s-capital-exodus-is-at-the-heart-of-coalition-collapse</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国总理奥拉夫·舒尔茨领导的分裂联盟难以阻止大规模的资本流失，而唐纳德·特朗普连任后，资本流失可能会加速。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-07/germany-s-capital-exodus-is-at-the-heart-of-coalition-collapse</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Nov 2024 06:51:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>刺激政策希望抵消特朗普风险 中国股市反弹</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-07/chinese-stocks-bounce-back-on-policy-hopes-promising-trade-data</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于强劲的出口数据和对更多政策刺激的希望超过了对唐纳德·特朗普第二任总统可能带来的贸易摩擦的担忧，中国股市从周三的下跌中强势反弹。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-07/chinese-stocks-bounce-back-on-policy-hopes-promising-trade-data</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Nov 2024 06:39:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>安赛乐米塔尔呼吁采取贸易措施应对中国出口</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-07/arcelormittal-says-market-unsustainable-but-sees-demand-pick-up</link>
      <description><![CDATA[安赛乐米塔尔公司呼吁采取更强有力的贸易措施来应对中国钢铁出口的大量增加，该公司认为这些措施导致市场不可持续，欧洲钢铁价格远低于边际成本。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-07/arcelormittal-says-market-unsustainable-but-sees-demand-pick-up</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Nov 2024 06:13:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>亚洲外汇交易员为美联储和中国令人失望的风险做好准备</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-07/reeling-asian-currency-market-has-to-face-fed-npc-risks-next</link>
      <description><![CDATA[亚洲货币交易员尚未从周三的抛售中恢复过来，但他们已经开始为即将出现的下一个宏观风险做准备。]]></description>
